divs: Sighting Detailsa week before sighting, my mother was dying at baltimore shock trauma, i had 10 month old little girl, asleep with me in bed, looked out window saw a star, and heard a voice in my head, can we have your baby, assumed it was ufo, not much phases me and said hell no, telepathically and "star" floated upwards and dissappeared. Week later, my dad was visiting mother at hospital, i realized i never took laundry off line, it was around 9 pm, went outside to retrieve laundry and felt like i was being watched, got sared for my child, went back in, 5 min. later my dad bursts thru doorway and said he saw a ufo, car stalled out at end of driveway and he saw several multi-olored lights take off at lightning speed. no-one believed him, idid, til it was in all the papers next day. soon after about 3 to 6 helicopters were in hoy pursuit around our house for several minutes. my sister got scared, i laughed and started playing close encounters of third kind on piano, while she screamed stop it. years later after death of both parents, my child developed what the doctors called an every day one of the mill cysts, but they wouldnt let me see it when they took it out. inside her upperarm you could feel it, it was sharp and pointy. also in 1986 i saw a phantom black cat, soon after that found 2 mutilated dogs at end of drive. our dog died, no rigormortis or bugs, buzzards, nothing. thats it.
